summary: LETTER FROM PETER HOKANSON OPPOSING THOSE PROVISIONS OF THE EARLY WARNING REPORTING (EWR)REGULATION THAT REQUIRES MANUFACTURERS THAT PRODUCE OVER 500 SMALL-TO-MEDIUM TRAILERS (THOSE WITH A GROSS WEIGHT  RATING, GVWR, OF UNDER 26000 POUNDS) TO ISSUE A COMPREHENSIVE EARLY WARNING REPORT TO NHTSA. SUCH REPORTING WOULD PUT MR HOPKANSON AND SOME OF HIS OTHER COLLEGUES IN TRAILER INDUSTRY OUT OF BUSINESS.  *AK
